('58','client','0','22','i want view indochine','Welcome back to Aurora Hotel Plaza, Administrator! It is a great pleasure to assist you again. \n\nRegarding the Indochine style, we have two exquisite room options available for you. Here are the details and current weekend rates:\n\n**1. Indochine Studio Apartment**\nPrice: 1,850,000 VND / night\n[IMAGE: https://aurorahotelplaza.com/assets/img/indochine-studio-apartment/indochine-studio-apartment-1.jpg]\n\n**2. Indochine Family Apartment**\nPrice: 2,550,000 VND / night\n[IMAGE: https://aurorahotelplaza.com/assets/img/indochine-family-apartment/indochine-family-apartment-1.jpg]\n\nBoth options feature our signature Indochine aesthetic, beautifully blending traditional Vietnamese elegance with modern comfort. \n\nTo make your stay even more perfect, may I suggest our private car pickup service (500,000 VND), or perhaps a relaxing session at our Spa and an evening at the Rooftop Bar? \n\nWhich room suits your preference, or would you like to proceed with a reservation?','glm-5','3095','success',NULL,'200',NULL,'2026-05-02 18:38:41'),
('59','client','0','22','i helpler booking now, i name Quang Long, arv 3/5/2026 to dep 6/5/2026 noting no smoking','Welcome back to Aurora Hotel Plaza! It is a great pleasure to assist you again. I have noted your booking request under the name Quang Long.\n\nHere are the details for your stay:\n- **Check-in:** May 3, 2026 (Sunday)\n- **Check-out:** May 6, 2026 (Wednesday)\n- **Duration:** 3 Nights\n- **Special Request:** Non-smoking room\n\nSince your arrival is on the weekend, I am delighted to offer you our best available rooms. All of our rooms are available in non-smoking configurations. Here are some excellent options for you:\n\n1. **Modern Studio Apartment** - 1,850,000 VND / night\n[IMAGE: https://aurorahotelplaza.com/assets/img/modern-studio-apartment/modern-studio-apartment-1.jpg]\n\n2. **Deluxe Room** - 1,900,000 VND / night\n[IMAGE: https://aurorahotelplaza.com/assets/img/deluxe/deluxe-room-aurora-1.jpg]\n\n3. **Aurora Studio** - 2,300,000 VND / night\n[IMAGE: https://aurorahotelplaza.com/assets/img/vip/vip-room-aurora-hotel-1.jpg]\n\nAll prices include VAT and a 5% service charge. Which room type would y','glm-5','3991','success',NULL,'200',NULL,'2026-05-02 18:43:18'),
