('131','22','0',NULL,'bot','Welcome back, Administrator! It is a true pleasure to see you again at Aurora Hotel Plaza. We noticed your last chat with us was on May 2nd, and we are delighted to have you return. \n\nHow may I assist you today? Whether you are looking to book a weekend getaway, arrange a relaxing session at our Spa, or reserve a table with a stunning view at our Rooftop Bar, I am entirely at your service.','text','0',NULL,'0',NULL,'2026-05-02 18:44:22'),
('132','22','7',NULL,'staff','i want helper booking dating people','text','0',NULL,'0',NULL,'2026-05-02 18:44:36'),
('133','22','0',NULL,'bot','Welcome back to Aurora Hotel Plaza, Administrator! We are absolutely delighted to see you again. \n\nRegarding your request, I must kindly inform you that arranging dating companions is not a service we provide at our hotel. \n\nHowever, if you are planning a romantic date or a special evening for you and your partner, we would be thrilled to assist you in creating the perfect setting! We can help you with:\n\n✨ **A romantic dinner or drinks** at our Rooftop Bar with stunning views.\n????‍♂️ **A relaxing couples\' session** at our Spa to unwind together.\n????️ **A luxurious stay** in one of our beautifully appointed rooms or apartments.\n\nWould you like me to help you book a room for the weekend, reserve a table at the Rooftop Bar, or arrange a Spa experience for your date? Please let me know how I can best assist you!','text','0',NULL,'0',NULL,'2026-05-02 18:44:50'),
('134','22','7',NULL,'staff','one more room classic and arrival in date now to depture 5/5/2026','text','0',NULL,'0',NULL,'2026-05-02 18:45:43'),
('135','22','0',NULL,'bot','Welcome back, Administrator! It is a pleasure to assist you again at Aurora Hotel Plaza. \n\nI would be happy to help you book one more Classical room from today (May 2, 2026) to May 5, 2026 (3 nights). Since today is the weekend, I have applied our current rates for you.\n\nWe have two types of Classical rooms available. Could you please confirm which one you would prefer?\n\n1. **Classical Premium** (Ideal for 2 guests)\n- Price: 2,050,000 VND / night\n- Total for 3 nights: 6,150,000 VND\n[IMAGE: https://aurorahotelplaza.com/assets/img/classical-premium-apartment/classical-premium-apartment-1.jpg]\n\n2. **Classical Family** (Spacious for families)\n- Price: 2,550,000 VND / night\n- Total for 3 nights: 7,650,000 VND\n[IMAGE: https://aurorahotelplaza.com/assets/img/classical-family-apartment/classical-family-apartment1.jpg]\n\n*(Note: All prices already include 5% service charge and 8% VAT, plus complimentary breakfast and access to our Pool, Gym, and Conference room).*\n\nSince your arrival is now (11:45 AM) and our standard check-in time is 2:00 PM, would you like to request an **Early Check-in**? The surcharge is only 50,000 VND. \n\nTo make your weekend stay even more relaxing, may I suggest our **Spa services** or a wonderful evening at our **Rooftop Bar**? We also offer a convenient **Car Transfer service** for 500,000 VND if you need transportation.\n\nPlease let me know your room choice and I will proceed with the booking immediately!','text','0',NULL,'0',NULL,'2026-05-02 18:46:14'),
('136','22','7',NULL,'staff','Classical Family one more','text','0',NULL,'0',NULL,'2026-05-02 18:46:39'),
('137','22','0',NULL,'bot','Welcome back, Administrator! It\'s a pleasure to assist you again at Aurora Hotel Plaza. \n\n[HỆ THỐNG ĐÃ TÌM THẤY ĐƠN HÀNG]\n\nI would be delighted to help you add one more **Classical Family** room to your reservation. As today is the weekend, the rate for the Classical Family room is **2,550,000đ** per night. It is a wonderfully spacious and elegant choice for families.\n\n[IMAGE: https://aurorahotelplaza.com/assets/img/classical-family-apartment/classical-family-apartment1.jpg]\n\nCould you please confirm the dates for this additional room so I can update your booking accordingly? \n\nTo make your upcoming stay even more convenient, may I suggest our private car pick-up/drop-off service for just 500,000đ? After a day of travel or meetings, our Spa and Rooftop Bar are also perfect places to unwind. Please let me know if you would like to add any of these services!','text','0',NULL,'0',NULL,'2026-05-02 18:46:54'),
