('204','25','0',NULL,'bot','Welcome to Aurora Hotel Plaza! I am your virtual concierge. How can I assist you with room bookings, services, or hotel information today?','text','0',NULL,'1','2026-05-11 12:38:53','2026-05-11 12:38:52'),
